{"id": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026__a2-late-chunking__0002", "text": "[Cybersecurity](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/veilig/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026__a2-late-chunking__0002", "source_slug": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026", "source_title": "NIS2 law is expected to come into effect in spring 2026", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026.html", "source_date": "2025-08-11", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 2}}
{"id": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026__a2-late-chunking__0003", "text": "After several delays, it is now almost certain: the Dutch implementation of the NIS2 directive will come into effect in the second quarter of 2026. Although the law was originally scheduled to come into effect on January 1, 2025, this proved to be unfeasible for many organizations.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026__a2-late-chunking__0003", "source_slug": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026", "source_title": "NIS2 law is expected to come into effect in spring 2026", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026.html", "source_date": "2025-08-11", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 3}}
{"id": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026__a2-late-chunking__0004", "text": "1. The legal text is ready - The consultation version was already published in 2023. There is political support and no substantive opposition.\n2. Pressure from Europe – The Netherlands is late in implementing and risks an infringement procedure.\n3. Sectors are already on the move – More than 100 industries are preparing. The demand for audits and certification is increasing.\n4. Infrastructure is ready - Reporting points, standards and guidance have largely been set up, including the NIS2 Quality Mark.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026__a2-late-chunking__0004", "source_slug": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026", "source_title": "NIS2 law is expected to come into effect in spring 2026", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026.html", "source_date": "2025-08-11", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 4}}
{"id": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026__a2-late-chunking__0005", "text": "Anyone who is already working on getting processes, supplier management and risk management in order is not doing so too early, but right on time. Experts emphasize: doing nothing now is no longer an option.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026__a2-late-chunking__0005", "source_slug": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026", "source_title": "NIS2 law is expected to come into effect in spring 2026", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026.html", "source_date": "2025-08-11", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 5}}
{"id": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026__a2-late-chunking__0006", "text": "About 1 in 5 entrepreneurs is confronted with cybercrime. Such a cyber incident can have major consequences for business operations, customers, suppliers or reputation. Taking appropriate measures is therefore important for every company.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026__a2-late-chunking__0006", "source_slug": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026", "source_title": "NIS2 law is expected to come into effect in spring 2026", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026.html", "source_date": "2025-08-11", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 6}}
{"id": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026__a2-late-chunking__0007", "text": "- Do you have an SME company and do you want to reduce your cyber risks? Then take a look at [Cyber ​​Fundament](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-voor-het-mkb/), especially for SME entrepreneurs.\n- Learn more about the 4-in-1 cyber solution [Cyber ​​Safe & Secure](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-veilig-en-zeker/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link) especially for large businesses and reduce your cyber risks.\n- Do you also want to [do business safely](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/veilig-ondernemen/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link)? View smart tools, useful articles and cyber webinars.\n- [Report fraud to us](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/prive/abnamro/veilig-banken/fraude-melden.html \"Report fraud\"), even if in doubt, after which our helpdesk will help you immediately.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026__a2-late-chunking__0007", "source_slug": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026", "source_title": "NIS2 law is expected to come into effect in spring 2026", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026.html", "source_date": "2025-08-11", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 7}}
{"id": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026__a2-late-chunking__0008", "text": "This article was produced in collaboration with [Samen Digitaal Veilig](https://www.samendigitaalveilig.nl).", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026__a2-late-chunking__0008", "source_slug": "nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026", "source_title": "NIS2 law is expected to come into effect in spring 2026", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/nis2-wet-gaat-naar-verwachting-in-werking-in-lente-2026.html", "source_date": "2025-08-11", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 8}}
